{"id":55,"ayahs":[{"number":38,"arabic":"هُنَالِكَ دَعَا زَكَرِيَّا رَبَّهُۥ ۖ قَالَ رَبِّ هَبْ لِى مِن لَّدُنكَ ذُرِّيَّةًۭ طَيِّبَةً ۖ إِنَّكَ سَمِيعُ ٱلدُّعَآءِ","translation":"In that self-same place, Zachariah prayed unto his Sustainer, saying: \"O my Sustainer! Bestow upon me [too], out of Thy grace, the gift of goodly offspring; for Thou, indeed, hearest all prayer.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/331.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":39839,"position":1,"arabic":"هُنَالِكَ","translation":"সেখানেই","audioUrl":"wbw/003_038_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39840,"position":2,"arabic":"دَعَا","translation":"দু'আ করল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_038_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39841,"position":3,"arabic":"زَكَرِيَّا","translation":"যাকারিয়া","audioUrl":"wbw/003_038_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39842,"position":4,"arabic":"رَبَّهُۥ ۖ","translation":"তার রবের কাছে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_038_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39844,"position":5,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"সে বলল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_038_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39845,"position":6,"arabic":"رَبِّ","translation":"''হে আমার রব","audioUrl":"wbw/003_038_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39846,"position":7,"arabic":"هَبْ","translation":"দাও","audioUrl":"wbw/003_038_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39847,"position":8,"arabic":"لِى","translation":"আমাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_038_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39848,"position":9,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_038_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39849,"position":10,"arabic":"لَّدُنكَ","translation":"তোমার নিকট","audioUrl":"wbw/003_038_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39850,"position":11,"arabic":"ذُرِّيَّةًۭ","translation":"বংশধর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_038_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39851,"position":12,"arabic":"طَيِّبَةً ۖ","translation":"পবিত্র (সৎ)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_038_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39853,"position":13,"arabic":"إِنَّكَ","translation":"তুমি নিশ্চয়","audioUrl":"wbw/003_038_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39854,"position":14,"arabic":"سَمِيعُ","translation":"শ্রবণকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/003_038_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39855,"position":15,"arabic":"ٱلدُّعَآءِ","translation":"দু'আ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_038_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39856,"position":16,"arabic":"٣٨","translation":"(৩৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":39,"arabic":"فَنَادَتْهُ ٱلْمَلَٰٓئِكَةُ وَهُوَ قَآئِمٌۭ يُصَلِّى فِى ٱلْمِحْرَابِ أَنَّ ٱللَّهَ يُبَشِّرُكَ بِيَحْيَىٰ مُصَدِّقًۢا بِكَلِمَةٍۢ مِّنَ ٱللَّهِ وَسَيِّدًۭا وَحَصُورًۭا وَنَبِيًّۭا مِّنَ ٱلصَّٰلِحِينَ","translation":"Thereupon, as he stood praying in the sanctuary, the angels called out unto him: \"God sends thee the glad tiding of [the birth of] John, who shall confirm the truth of a word from God, and [shall be] outstanding among men, and utterly chaste, and a prophet from among the righteous.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/332.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":40631,"position":1,"arabic":"فَنَادَتْهُ","translation":"তাকে তখন ডেকে বলল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_039_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40632,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْمَلَـٰٓئِكَةُ","translation":"ফেরেশতারা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_039_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40633,"position":3,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","translation":"যখন সে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_039_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40634,"position":4,"arabic":"قَآئِمٌۭ","translation":"দন্ডায়মান হয়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_039_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40635,"position":5,"arabic":"يُصَلِّى","translation":"সলাত পড়ছিল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_039_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40636,"position":6,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_039_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40637,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْمِحْرَابِ","translation":"তার কক্ষে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_039_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40638,"position":8,"arabic":"أَنَّ","translation":"''যে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_039_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40639,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_039_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40640,"position":10,"arabic":"يُبَشِّرُكَ","translation":"সুসংবাদ দিচ্ছেন তো্মাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_039_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40641,"position":11,"arabic":"بِيَحْيَىٰ","translation":"ইয়াহইয়ার","audioUrl":"wbw/003_039_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40642,"position":12,"arabic":"مُصَدِّقًۢا","translation":"সত্যায়নকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/003_039_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40643,"position":13,"arabic":"بِكَلِمَةٍۢ","translation":"একটা বাণীর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_039_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40644,"position":14,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"পক্ষ হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_039_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40645,"position":15,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_039_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40646,"position":16,"arabic":"وَسَيِّدًۭا","translation":"ও নেতা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_039_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40647,"position":17,"arabic":"وَحَصُورًۭا","translation":"এবং সাধু বৈশিষ্ট্যের","audioUrl":"wbw/003_039_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40648,"position":18,"arabic":"وَنَبِيًّۭا","translation":"ও নবী","audioUrl":"wbw/003_039_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40649,"position":19,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"অন্যতম","audioUrl":"wbw/003_039_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40650,"position":20,"arabic":"ٱلصَّـٰلِحِينَ","translation":"সৎকর্মশীলদের","audioUrl":"wbw/003_039_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40651,"position":21,"arabic":"٣٩","translation":"(৩৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":40,"arabic":"قَالَ رَبِّ أَنَّىٰ يَكُونُ لِى غُلَٰمٌۭ وَقَدْ بَلَغَنِىَ ٱلْكِبَرُ وَٱمْرَأَتِى عَاقِرٌۭ ۖ قَالَ كَذَٰلِكَ ٱللَّهُ يَفْعَلُ مَا يَشَآءُ","translation":"[Zachariah] exclaimed: \"O my Sustainer! How can I have a son when old age has already overtaken me, and my wife is barren?\" Answered [the angel]: \"Thus it is: God does what He wills.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/333.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":41446,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"সে বলল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_040_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41447,"position":2,"arabic":"رَبِّ","translation":"''হে আমার রব","audioUrl":"wbw/003_040_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41448,"position":3,"arabic":"أَنَّىٰ","translation":"কিরুপে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_040_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41449,"position":4,"arabic":"يَكُونُ","translation":"আমার হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_040_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41450,"position":5,"arabic":"لِى","translation":"ছেলে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_040_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41451,"position":6,"arabic":"غُلَـٰمٌۭ","translation":"এবং","audioUrl":"wbw/003_040_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41452,"position":7,"arabic":"وَقَدْ","translation":"নিশ্চয়","audioUrl":"wbw/003_040_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41453,"position":8,"arabic":"بَلَغَنِىَ","translation":"আমার পৌছে গেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_040_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41454,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْكِبَرُ","translation":"বার্ধক্য","audioUrl":"wbw/003_040_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41455,"position":10,"arabic":"وَٱمْرَأَتِى","translation":"ও আমার স্ত্রী","audioUrl":"wbw/003_040_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41456,"position":11,"arabic":"عَاقِرٌۭ ۖ","translation":"বন্ধ্যা''","audioUrl":"wbw/003_040_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41458,"position":12,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"তিনি বললেন","audioUrl":"wbw/003_040_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41459,"position":13,"arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ","translation":"''এভাবেই","audioUrl":"wbw/003_040_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41460,"position":14,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_040_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41461,"position":15,"arabic":"يَفْعَلُ","translation":"করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/003_040_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41462,"position":16,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_040_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41463,"position":17,"arabic":"يَشَآءُ","translation":"তিনি ইচ্ছা করেন''","audioUrl":"wbw/003_040_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41464,"position":18,"arabic":"٤٠","translation":"(৪০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":41,"arabic":"قَالَ رَبِّ ٱجْعَل لِّىٓ ءَايَةًۭ ۖ قَالَ ءَايَتُكَ أَلَّا تُكَلِّمَ ٱلنَّاسَ ثَلَٰثَةَ أَيَّامٍ إِلَّا رَمْزًۭا ۗ وَٱذْكُر رَّبَّكَ كَثِيرًۭا وَسَبِّحْ بِٱلْعَشِىِّ وَٱلْإِبْكَٰرِ","translation":"[Zachariah] prayed: \"O my Sustainer! Appoint a sign for me!\" Said [the angel]: \"Thy sign shall be that for three days thou wilt not speak unto men other than by gestures. And remember thy Sustainer unceasingly, and extol His limitless glory by night and by day.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/334.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":42229,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"সে বলল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_041_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42230,"position":2,"arabic":"رَبِّ","translation":"''হে আমার রব","audioUrl":"wbw/003_041_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42231,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱجْعَل","translation":"দাও","audioUrl":"wbw/003_041_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42232,"position":4,"arabic":"لِّىٓ","translation":"আমার জন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/003_041_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42233,"position":5,"arabic":"ءَايَةًۭ ۖ","translation":"কোন নিদর্শন''","audioUrl":"wbw/003_041_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42235,"position":6,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"তিনি বললেন","audioUrl":"wbw/003_041_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42236,"position":7,"arabic":"ءَايَتُكَ","translation":"তোমার নিদর্শন","audioUrl":"wbw/003_041_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42237,"position":8,"arabic":"أَلَّا","translation":"এটা যে না","audioUrl":"wbw/003_041_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42238,"position":9,"arabic":"تُكَلِّمَ","translation":"কথা বলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_041_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42239,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلنَّاسَ","translation":"মানুষের (সাথে)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_041_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42240,"position":11,"arabic":"ثَلَـٰثَةَ","translation":"তিন","audioUrl":"wbw/003_041_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42241,"position":12,"arabic":"أَيَّامٍ","translation":"দিন (পর্যন্ত)","audioUrl":"wbw/003_041_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42242,"position":13,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/003_041_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42243,"position":14,"arabic":"رَمْزًۭا ۗ","translation":"ইঙ্গিত","audioUrl":"wbw/003_041_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42245,"position":15,"arabic":"وَٱذْكُر","translation":"এবং তুমি স্মরণ কর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_041_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42246,"position":16,"arabic":"رَّبَّكَ","translation":"তোমার রবকে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_041_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42247,"position":17,"arabic":"كَثِيرًۭا","translation":"বেশী বেশী","audioUrl":"wbw/003_041_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42248,"position":18,"arabic":"وَسَبِّحْ","translation":"ও তূমি তসবিহ কর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_041_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42249,"position":19,"arabic":"بِٱلْعَشِىِّ","translation":"সন্ধ্যার সময়","audioUrl":"wbw/003_041_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42250,"position":20,"arabic":"وَٱلْإِبْكَـٰرِ","translation":"ও প্রভাতে''","audioUrl":"wbw/003_041_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42251,"position":21,"arabic":"٤١","translation":"(৪১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":42,"arabic":"وَإِذْ قَالَتِ ٱلْمَلَٰٓئِكَةُ يَٰمَرْيَمُ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ ٱصْطَفَىٰكِ وَطَهَّرَكِ وَٱصْطَفَىٰكِ عَلَىٰ نِسَآءِ ٱلْعَٰلَمِينَ","translation":"AND LO! The angels said: \"O Mary! Behold, God has elected thee and made thee pure, and raised thee above all the women of the world.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/335.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":43281,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذْ","translation":"ও যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/003_042_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43282,"position":2,"arabic":"قَالَتِ","translation":"বলেছিল","audioUrl":"wbw/003_042_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43283,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْمَلَـٰٓئِكَةُ","translation":"ফেরেশতারা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_042_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43284,"position":4,"arabic":"يَـٰمَرْيَمُ","translation":"''যে মারইয়াম","audioUrl":"wbw/003_042_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43285,"position":5,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়","audioUrl":"wbw/003_042_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43286,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_042_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43287,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱصْطَفَىٰكِ","translation":"তোমাকে মনোনীত করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/003_042_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43288,"position":8,"arabic":"وَطَهَّرَكِ","translation":"এবং তোমাকে পবিত্র করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/003_042_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43289,"position":9,"arabic":"وَٱصْطَفَىٰكِ","translation":"এবং তোমাকে শ্রেষ্ঠত্ব দিয়েছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/003_042_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43290,"position":10,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_042_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43291,"position":11,"arabic":"نِسَآءِ","translation":"নারীদের","audioUrl":"wbw/003_042_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43292,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلْعَـٰلَمِينَ","translation":"সারা বিশ্বের''","audioUrl":"wbw/003_042_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43293,"position":13,"arabic":"٤٢","translation":"(৪২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":43,"arabic":"يَٰمَرْيَمُ ٱقْنُتِى لِرَبِّكِ وَٱسْجُدِى وَٱرْكَعِى مَعَ ٱلرَّٰكِعِينَ","translation":"O Mary! Remain thou truly devout unto thy Sustainer, and prostrate thyself in worship, and bow down with those who bow down [before Him].\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/336.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":44091,"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰمَرْيَمُ","translation":"''হে মারইয়াম","audioUrl":"wbw/003_043_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44092,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱقْنُتِى","translation":"তুমি অনুগত হও","audioUrl":"wbw/003_043_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44093,"position":3,"arabic":"لِرَبِّكِ","translation":"তোমার রবের জন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/003_043_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44094,"position":4,"arabic":"وَٱسْجُدِى","translation":"এবং তুমি সিজদা কর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_043_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44095,"position":5,"arabic":"وَٱرْكَعِى","translation":"ও তূমি রুকু কর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_043_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44096,"position":6,"arabic":"مَعَ","translation":"সাথে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_043_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44097,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلرَّٰكِعِينَ","translation":"রুকুকারীদের''","audioUrl":"wbw/003_043_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44098,"position":8,"arabic":"٤٣","translation":"(৪৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":44,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ مِنْ أَنۢبَآءِ ٱلْغَيْبِ نُوحِيهِ إِلَيْكَ ۚ وَمَا كُنتَ لَدَيْهِمْ إِذْ يُلْقُونَ أَقْلَٰمَهُمْ أَيُّهُمْ يَكْفُلُ مَرْيَمَ وَمَا كُنتَ لَدَيْهِمْ إِذْ يَخْتَصِمُونَ","translation":"This account of something that was beyond the reach of thy perception We [now] reveal unto thee: for thou wert not with them when they drew lots as to which of them should be Mary's guardian, and thou wert not with them when they contended [about it] with one another.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/337.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":44211,"position":1,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এটা","audioUrl":"wbw/003_044_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44212,"position":2,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"অংশবিশেষ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_044_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44213,